OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,FA Co Londonderry man accused of
OL,7,Fassaulting another man at Strabane
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court has been remanded
OL,9,Fin custody.
OL,11,FDungannon Magistrates' Court heard on
OL,12,FSaturday morning that the incident
OL,13,Fcame before a planned hearing for a
OL,14,Fman charged with the murder of Stephen
OL,15,FHolmes in Strabane in 2025.
OL,17,FA kettle of boiling water was thrown
OL,18,Fover a man who was treated in hospital
OL,19,Ffor burn injuries to his face and
OL,20,Fupper body.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,FThe Dungannon court heard on Saturday
OL,7,Fmorning that the accused, Corie
OL,8,FMcKenna, 34, of Sheskin Park in
OL,9,FGreysteel, denies the assault charges.
OL,11,FThe court heard he has been charged
OL,12,Fwith assault occasioning actual bodily
OL,13,Fharm, maliciously attempting to cause
OL,14,Fgrievous bodily harm to a victim and
OL,15,Fpossession of an offensive weapon with
OL,16,Fintent, namely a kettle of boiling
OL,17,Fwater.
OL,19,FAsked if he understood the charges,
OL,20,FMcKenna responded: "Yes, I do."
OL,26,@|D@TOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,FA detective constable said she
OL,7,Fbelieves the accused can be connected
OL,8,Fwith the charges.
OL,10,FOutlining the circumstances, she said
OL,11,Fa preliminary hearing had been due to
OL,12,Fbe heard in the murder case at the
OL,13,FStrabane court.
OL,15,F"It attracted the attention of both
OL,16,Fthe family of the defendant as well as
OL,17,Fof the victim. Shortly before 11am
OL,18,Fpolice received a report of an
OL,19,Fincident inside the courthouse,
OL,20,Foutside the courtroom," she said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,F"It was alleged that the brother of
OL,7,Fthe defendant was approached by a male
OL,8,Fwho had a kettle of boiled water. He
OL,9,Fthrew the water at him from a very
OL,10,Fshort range ` within one metre. The
OL,11,Fwater connected with his face, arm,
OL,12,Fneck and back, causing burn injuries."
OL,14,FShe said the victim and his partner
OL,15,Fnamed the defendant as the man
OL,16,Fresponsible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,F"He was wearing a very distinctive
OL,7,Forange T-shirt, and immediately after
OL,8,Fthe incident he left the scene, and a
OL,9,Fscuffle between the two families
OL,10,Foccurred," she said.
OL,12,F"The victim was treated by paramedics,
OL,13,Fand brought in an ambulance to
OL,14,FAltnagelvin Hospital where he was
OL,15,Ftreated, and then he was transferred
OL,16,Fto the Royal Victoria Hospital (in
OL,17,FBelfast), to the burn unit for further
OL,18,Fassessment."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]tD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,FShe said McKenna was located at his
OL,7,Fhome at 11.45pm and arrested, and in
OL,8,Finterview said he had been at the
OL,9,Fcourt and there was a verbal exchange,
OL,10,Fbut denied involvement in the assault.
OL,12,FBail was opposed by police, who have
OL,13,Ffurther witnesses to interview, and
OL,14,Fdescribed the victim as "being in
OL,15,Ffear" of McKenna and further
OL,16,Frepercussions.
OL,26,@vD@YOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,FAsked whether the two were known to
OL,7,Feach other, the detective constable
OL,8,Fsaid: "I believe just in connection to
OL,9,Fthe incident at court, it's a murder
OL,10,Finvestigation."
OL,12,FThe judge described "serious charges",
OL,13,Fadding it was "not a case I would be
OL,14,Fminded to grant bail on".
OL,16,FDefence barrister Joe McCann, acting
OL,17,Ffor McKenna, said he did not dispute
OL,18,Fthat assessment but stressed that his
OL,19,Fclient is entitled to a presumption of
OL,20,Finnocence.
OL,26,@pD@GOUrD@OO]tD@UOUtD@eO]uD@OOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,F"It was a busy court on Thursday, a
OL,7,Flot of people there?" he put to the
OL,8,Fdetective constable, who responded: "I
OL,9,Fwasn't in attendance but I believe so."
OL,11,FMr McCann said he understands police
OL,12,Fwill have to speak to a number of
OL,13,Fwitnesses who were in the foyer, and
OL,14,Fnot all will know McKenna.
OL,16,F"Is it a fair suggestion it might take
OL,17,Fa very long time?" he asked the
OL,18,Fdetective constable, who responded: "I
OL,19,Fcan't answer in relation to that, I
OL,20,Fwould need to check."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@UO]pD@eOUqD@gO]xD@AOUyD@RO]zD@
OL,26,AeOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,FHe asked if there was CCTV footage of
OL,7,Fthe incident, and was told there was
OL,8,Fnot.
OL,10,FHe also pointed out McKenna lives a
OL,11,F"distance apart" from the victim.
OL,13,F"I don't for one moment suggest that
OL,14,Fthis isn't a serious allegation ` it's
OL,15,Fserious in many ways, particularly
OL,16,Fserious because of its location, the
OL,17,Ffact that it allegedly took place at a
OL,18,Fcourt," he said.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@PO]uD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,F"But the fact remains this man has
OL,7,Fdenied that he carried out this
OL,8,Fassault. He is entitled to the
OL,9,Fpresumption of innocence, he has
OL,10,Fdisputed the identification evidence
OL,11,Fthat has been put forward.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,F"It seems to me that this
OL,7,Finvestigation is at a very early
OL,8,Fstage, it probably is going to take
OL,9,Fquite a long time for police to
OL,10,Fconclude their inquiries. There has
OL,11,Fbeen no suggestion that the defendant
OL,12,Fcould interfere with those inquiries
OL,13,Fas many of the witnesses that police
OL,14,Fare going to speak to wouldn't be
OL,15,Fknown to him.
OL,17,F"He has two children under the age of
OL,18,Fseven that he sees regularly, he has
OL,19,Fties in the community, so we say it is
OL,20,Fnot a risk of flight.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,F"We say that with very stringent bail
OL,7,Fconditions and given how long this
OL,8,Fcase is likely to take to come to
OL,9,Fcourt, with all the delays that are in
OL,10,Fthe criminal justice system, that you
OL,11,Fcould safely grant him bail."
OL,13,FThe judge refused, saying she has
OL,14,Fconcerns about the seriousness of the
OL,15,Foffences, the fear of the victim and
OL,16,Fother witnesses still to be spoken to
OL,17,Fby police.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776517870
OL,3,CMan accused of boiling water attack at
OL,4,Ccourt remanded in custody
OL,6,F"But it is the sheer circumstances and
OL,7,Fthe seriousness of the assault, with
OL,8,Fburn injuries, and there is a
OL,9,Fsituation where there are potentially
OL,10,Fother witnesses to be spoken to," she
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FThe case is next to be mentioned at
OL,14,FDungannon Magistrates' Court on May 13.
